msgstr "Saamsmelt instellings"

msgid ""
"Double click to set pages you want to merge (ex: 2 or 5-23 or 2,5-7,12-)"
msgstr ""
"Dubbel kliek te stel bladsye wat jy wil om saamsmelt (ex: 2 of 5-23 of 2,5-"
